p.-text Chi includes a fully responsive 12-column grid layout system. Built on the flexbox standards, the Chi grid system allows for complex layouts with minimal markup and styles.

h3 Basics

p.-text Grid layouts are defined as a grid container that is composed of one or more rows of columns.

h4 Automatic Layout

p.-text By default, columns within a grid container will occupy an equal amount of horizontal space. Content within those columns is constrained to the width of the column (i.e. the column will not widen to accommodate its contents).

